Revision history for Perl extension App-sync_cpantesters

1.111470  2011-05-27 22:35:40 Europe/Vienna
    - separated command-line processing into bin/sync_cpantesters
    - the module has been turned into a class; the former options are now
      accessors
    - added a trigger 'dist.filter', per Class::Trigger

1.110730  2011-03-14 10:49:24 Europe/Vienna
    - get rid of "Wide character in print at ..." (thanks trapd00r)

1.100830  2010-03-24 22:52:50 Europe/Vienna
    - added --ignore option to filter out reports for unwanted distributions

1.100710  2010-03-12 14:17:51 Europe/Vienna
    - adapted scraper (etc.) to new HTML contents
    - converted the distribution to Dist::Zilla-style
    - moved the code to App::perlzonji; bin/sync_cpantesters is just a thin
      wrapper
    - documented the subroutines

0.05 Sat Jul 18 20:07:13 CEST 2009 (Marcel Gruenauer <marcel@cpan.org>)
     - Changed dist style and Changes back to standard. People didn't like it -
       the nail that sticks out gets hammered down.
     - Added standard test files; this will also help with CPANTS.
     - Changed scraper to match new HTML layout

0.04  Thu, 29 May 2008 12:00:00 -0000 (Marcel Gruenauer <marcel@cpan.org>)
     - set the version to 0.04
     - now uses LWP::UserAgent::ProgressBar
     - .shipit: fixed svk.tagpattern

0.03  Sat, 24 Nov 2007 16:39:38 -0000 (Marcel Gruenauer <marcel@cpan.org>)
     - set the version to 0.03
     - fixed bug in how directories are deleted - before, the whole base dir
       was deleted

